  m_text: "- Ch\xE8 Hu\u1EBF is a traditional dessert from the city of Hu\u1EBF in
    Central Vietnam.\n\n- It is often sold by street vendors and enjoyed as a snack
    or dessert rather than a full meal.\n\n- The dish has many variations using various
    kinds of bean, jelly, coconut milk, lotus seeds, or tapioca.\n\n- Ch\xE8 Hu\u1EBF
    reflects the elegant food culture of the former imperial city."
