  m_text: "- C\u01A1m T\u1EA5m is a Southern Vietnamese rice dish made from broken
    rice grains.\n\n- It became popular because broken rice was once considered a
    cheaper ingredient for workers and farmers.\n\n- The meal is usually served with
    grilled pork, egg meatloaf, pickled vegetables, and fish sauce.\n\n- Nowadays,
    it is one of the most common everyday meals in Ho Chi Minh City."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f6b83f304dc3a98448bbbbe575dcc972, type: 2}
